HB 4040
1 options and other support resources available for members who have mental illnesses or substance
2 use disorders.
3 (r) Each coordinated care organization works with the Tribal Advisory Council established in
4 ORS 414.581 and has a dedicated tribal liaison, selected by the council, to:
